                        <div class="front">
                            <h3>What did Vancouver's expedition actually achieve?</h3>
                        </div>
                        <div class="back">
                            <a href="#card2" class="card-skip-link offScreen">Skip to the next card</a>
                            <div class="responsive-wrapper">
                                <iframe id="vimeo1" class="no-js-hide vimeo" title="European Navigation Video" src="https://player.vimeo.com/video/483195238?color=ee314a&title=0&byline=0&portrait=0&speed=1&playsinline=true" allow="autoplay; fullscreen" allowfullscreen></iframe>
                                <noscript>
